From db6aef404bd78558304ddefed03899025bee4b9d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kol Crooks <kol.crooks@datadoghq.com>
Date: Tue, 5 May 2026 09:13:31 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 7: configurable Anthropic base URL

Adds krt.configureAnthropicBaseUrl command + readBaseUrl/writeBaseUrl
helpers so orgs that route Anthropic traffic through a corporate
gateway (e.g. Datadog) can override the default api.anthropic.com.
Tour generator reads the URL at request time and appends /v1/messages.
Empty / default value clears the override.
